oralist and a brilliant oralist here

00:16:01.360 --> 00:16:04.710
in DC who he felt would
do a better job.

00:16:04.710 --> 00:16:06.690
That's how committed Al was.

00:16:06.690 --> 00:16:10.300
He actually stepped down and didn't
argue the case because he wanted

00:16:10.300 --> 00:16:13.500
to do right by his clients.

00:16:13.500 --> 00:16:14.800
&gt;&gt; Travis Painter: Wow.

00:16:14.800 --> 00:16:16.240
And Debbie, what was
your involvement

00:16:16.240 --> 00:16:21.030
with the LGBT community before
writing, during writing,

00:16:21.030 --> 00:16:23.860
and now a year after
