00:44:53.030 --> 00:44:55.780
You can go in there
to see highlights

00:44:55.780 --> 00:44:57.650
about the Walt Whitman
papers, for example,

00:44:57.650 --> 00:45:01.820
or Leonard Bernstein's collection,
or a vast range of American poets

00:45:01.820 --> 00:45:03.930
who have read their work
here at the Library.

00:45:03.930 --> 00:45:05.780
Our collections are vast.

00:45:05.780 --> 00:45:07.970
As you know, we have
over 160 million items.

00:45:07.970 --> 00:45:10.980
